{"tid":1656714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［推上熱門］一名學生對社會運動的感受","createTime":"2019-10-15T17:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T17:47:41.000Z","uid":313174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ec31e49bda67c94f9a825b271c7a6e977b0601a5","tid":1656714,"uid":313174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:30:37.000Z","msg":"感謝每一個對生命不離不棄的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n每個生命的消逝與隕落都讓我們痛心難過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝每一個對青年人施予援手的香港人，<br />\n<br />\n每個聲嘶力竭的呼救都讓我們淚流滿面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝每一個對真相追尋到底的香港人，<br />\n<br />\n每段消息與事實的荒謬都足以讓我們懷疑人生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝每一個為公義而發聲的香港人，<br />\n<br />\n每個赤子之心都值得予以尊重。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝每一個無所畏懼地走上街頭的香港人，<br />\n<br />\n每一個人都是我的家人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝每一個無畏無懼走上前線的手足，<br />\n<br />\n每一個人都是站在世界最前沿對抗極權的勇士，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好榮幸同大家出生於同一片土地，<br />\n<br />\n見證最好的時代，也見證最壞的時代。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後請大家永遠不要忘記，在這個盛夏，<br />\n<br />\n被拘捕，被入獄，被失蹤，被殺害的真香港人。<br />\n<br />\n因為只有將他人的經歷，當作自己的經歷，<br />\n<br />\n將他人的痛苦，視之為自己的痛苦，<br />\n<br />\n我們的命運共同體才會誕生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請大家將這個故事講給下一代，<br />\n<br />\n並勸勉他們珍惜自由與民主的可貴。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa3670da0e8f911e945d3fe4b98fb3fbaabed2c","tid":1656714,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjbDGh.jpg&h=e5447ac9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"15e8c451c10a8d3767cf95ca80f68c03f5a6800e","tid":1656714,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36uGjB5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36uGjB5.jpg&h=9d83ffec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dxhdaJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdxhdaJL.jpg&h=e5c0d53a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8e4OJ3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8e4OJ3M.jpg&h=a0cedb07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5HGhCoM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5HGhCoM.jpg&h=7766d02f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e5270befa3d3e2f50285c5cb875600d0c5bf3b9","tid":1656714,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"求幫推 p牌仔推唔喐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【簡易文宣】本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ae8fbbda67df923a28c6b850f0c3810620c59b0b","tid":1656714,"uid":313174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e5270befa3d3e2f50285c5cb875600d0c5bf3b9","tid":1656714,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"求幫推 p牌仔推唔喐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【簡易文宣】本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:47:41.000Z","msg":"推唔到"}]}